      <li>Helme, N. A. 2007. Botanical report: Fine scale vegetation mapping in the Upper Breede River Valley. Report for CapeNature, as part of the C.A.P.E. programme.</li>
      <li>Mucina, L., Rutherford, M.C. 2006. The vegetation of South Africa, Lesotho and Swaziland. Strelitzia 19.</li>
      <li>Manning, J., 2018. Field Guide to Fynbos</li>
      <li>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renosterveld</li>
      <li>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robertson_Karoo</li>
      <li>http://pza.sanbi.org/vegetation (and related links)</li>
    </ul>

  </article>
</section>
